Renew Policy Business Process

When it's time to renew your policy, you get an email with a renewal link. Enter some details for the renewal and it's done.

The Renew Policy OmniScript is available in OmniScripts under Type - insFSC/RenewPolicy and Version Name - Renew Policy FSC.

How Renew Policy Works

The Renew Policy workflow renews your policy.
- The OmniScript takes a policy Id and uses services to retrieve data about the vehicles insured by this policy and the corresponding coverages for them.
- It displays the vehicle and coverage details, lets users modify coverages, and updates the price on the user interface if modified.
- It creates a renewed policy, updates the old policy, and displays information about the renewed policy.

What's in the Renew Policy OmniScript

The Renew Policy OmniScript has components to get insured items and policy coverages, set renewal dates and policy ID, configure coverages, and update policies.

How to Renew a Policy

Customer services reps, policyholders, and brokers can renew policies three different ways:

- Renew a Policy from the Policy UI
- Renew Policies from the Digital Experience Site
- Renew a Policy Through Email
